source(output(
		{Account Name} as string,
		SlugName as string,
		{Account ID} as string,
		{Parent ID Number} as string,
		{Parent First Name} as string,
		{Parent Last Name} as string,
		{Parent Email} as string,
		{Student ID Number} as string,
		{Student First Name} as string,
		{Student Last Name} as string,
		{Student Email} as string,
		Address1 as string,
		City as string,
		{State/Province} as string,
		{Zip Code} as string,
		Country as string,
		Phone as string,
		{Entry Term} as string,
		{Entry Year} as string,
		{Student Type} as string,
		Stage as string,
		Flag_International as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	isolationLevel: 'READ_UNCOMMITTED',
	format: 'table',
	staged: false) ~> source
source derive(filename = 'partnerintegration/'+'campusesp/'+'outbound/'+SlugName+'/'+SlugName+'.csv',
		EntryTerm = concat({Entry Term},' ',{Entry Year})) ~> Filename
Filename sink(allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	rowUrlColumn:'filename',
	umask: 0022,
	preCommands: [],
	postCommands: [],
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true,
	mapColumn(
		vendor_key = {Parent ID Number},
		first_name = {Parent First Name},
		last_name = {Parent Last Name},
		Email = {Parent Email},
		{Student ID Number},
		{Student First Name},
		{Student Last Name},
		{Student Email},
		Address1,
		City,
		State = {State/Province},
		Zip = {Zip Code},
		country_code = Country,
		Phone,
		stage = Stage,
		{Entry Term} = EntryTerm,
		{student type} = {Student Type},
		filename,
		Flag_International
	)) ~> sink

SELECT      [id] as [Id]
           ,[seq_no] as [SeqNo]
           ,[src_object_type] as [SrcObjectType]
           ,[src_object_name] as [SrcObjectName]
           ,[primary_key] as [PrimaryKey]
           ,[source_delta_column] as [SourceDeltaColumn]
           ,[cdc_key] as [CDC_Key]
           ,[schema] as [Schema]
           ,[destination_table_name] as [DestinationTableName]
           ,[container] as [Container]
           ,[file_path] as [FilePath]

SELECt distinct a.RESPONSE_ID as po_responseid, b.po_accountName FROM staging.em_historical_data_all a (nolock)
inner join dbo.flag_fplus_files b (nolock) on b.po_responseid = a.RESPONSE_ID

sqlReaderQuery.value:
select * from [staging].[em_historical_data_all]  WITH (NOLOCK) 
where response_id= '@{item().po_responseid}' and crm_flag=1 and rejected_row=0

select distinct a.unique_id,b.contact_id from [staging].[em_historical_data_all] (nolock) a
inner join  [alignment].[contact_ref_historical] (nolock) b
on a.unique_id = b.historical_source_key
where [MODIFIED_FILENAME]='@{activity('filename').output.value[0].modified_filename}'
and a.crm_flag=1 and a.rejected_row=0

select top 1 acc.name as po_accountName,cstord.po_responseid,cstord.po_accountmodel,
CASE
    WHEN cststat.po_fqtcustomerorderstatusId = 'C0D9A877-69C3-EB11-A81A-000D3AF522D6' THEN 'D16830EE-8CC3-EB11-A81A-000D3AF522D6'
    WHEN cststat.po_fqtcustomerorderstatusId= '5FD3E375-50AF-EB11-A9C6-000D3A062608' THEN '16B5057C-50AF-EB11-A9C6-000D3A062608'
END as newOrderStatus
,cstord.po_fqtcustomerorderId
from [dbo].[po_fqtcustomerorderBase] as cstord
left join dbo.[po_accountmodelBase] as accmod
on cstord.[po_accountmodel] = accmod.[po_accountmodelId]
join  [dbo].[AccountBase] as acc
on cstord.[po_account] = acc.AccountId
left join  [dbo].[po_fqtcustomerorderstatusBase] as cststat
on cstord.po_orderstatus=cststat.po_fqtcustomerorderstatusId
left join [dbo].[po_scoringmodelBase] as scmod
on accmod.po_modeltype = scmod.[po_scoringmodelId]
where ((cststat.[po_name] = 'Received for Modeling' or 
cststat.[po_name] = 'Received for Scoring') and ( scmod.po_name = 'Prospect'))
and cstord.po_responseid = '@{item().po_responseid}'

dependsOn.activity: check if record is present in file metadata

 WITH (NOLOCK)

where [MODIFIED_FILENAME]='@{activity('filename').output.value[0].modified_filename}'

select top 1 acc.name as po_accountName,cstord.po_responseid,cstord.po_accountmodel,
CASE
    WHEN cststat.po_fqtcustomerorderstatusId = 'C0D9A877-69C3-EB11-A81A-000D3AF522D6' THEN 'D16830EE-8CC3-EB11-A81A-000D3AF522D6'
    WHEN cststat.po_fqtcustomerorderstatusId= '5FD3E375-50AF-EB11-A9C6-000D3A062608' THEN '16B5057C-50AF-EB11-A9C6-000D3A062608'

,cstord.po_fqtcustomerorderId
